title: 2018 Week 16 Preview
itunes:title: 2018 Week 16 Preview
description:
A room filled with heroes- Dan Hanzus, Nick Shook, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal preview all the upcoming week 16 games. Rhode Island is ATN’s biggest fan, but why? (2:00) Will the Browns make the playoffs? (21:23) What does Josh Gordon leaving the Patriots mean for their season? (42:08) Buckle up, week 16 is upon us!
